# How to Configure {{ project_name }}

This guide shows you how to set up and customize {{ project_name }} for your project.

## Basic Configuration

```python
from {{ package_name }} import [MainClass]

instance = [MainClass](
    option_1="value",
    option_2=True,
)
```

## Configuration File

```yaml
# config.yaml
{{ package_name }}:
  option_1: value
  option_2: true
```

